core.each.shortDescription: Iterate over each key in a dictionary, where each key is a propery of the dictionary.

params.name: callback
params.description: Function to call for each item. Arguments passed: current key, current item, dictionary.

core.generateKey.shortDescription: Generate a random key based on the length and digits requested.

params.name: length
params.description: Length of string to use as key.

params.name: digits
params.description: String of digits to use when generating key.

core.unpack.longDescription: The target will have the key-value pairs appended, or overwritten if the key-value pair already exists.
core.unpack.shortDescription: Unpack a dictionary to a target.

core.request.shortDescription: Request for data from server using HTTP requests.

params.name: callback
params.description: Callback function to call when response is returned, arguments given are `data`, `status`, `state` and `type`.

params.name: type
params.description: Type of request to use (like `GET`, `POST` and `PUT`). Default: `"GET"`.

params.name: body
params.description: Body to send in request (mainly just for `POST` requests). Default: `null`.

return.description: Value of parameter. `null` if parameter is not found.
